+ New Lua Shell
  > You can now use our fancy new Lua interactive prompt on your quick tests.

+ Uninstaller
  > If you don't like Flip or don't want to use it anymore, you can now uninstall it easily.

* Bios Bootloader Logo
  > Flip now have a Bios Logo, you can see it when booting your device.

+ Password Lock
  > You can change the password on the settings app.

* Shell Sandboxing
  > Shell now protects the system folders and files.
    You can modify system files using scripts if you really want.